text: Erica Lynn O' Keith (born December 19, 1984 in Los Angeles, California) is an actress best known for her role in the Nickelodeon sitcom Romeo!. She has also guest starred in Close to Home and Scrubs. She is currently on the McDonald's Southwest Salad commercial as the cashier. She was also one of the girls on the bleachers in Corbin Bleu's music video for "Push It to the Limit".
